 "html": "<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\">I grew up with oat crunchies. &nbsp;There's something comforting about this kind of biscuit. &nbsp;The trouble with it is, once you start eating you can't stop.</p>\n\n\n<div data-recipe-slot=\"1\"></div>\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter\"><a href=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Coq-Au-Vin-en-oatskoekies-blog-069.jpg\"><img src=\"/media/uploads/2017/10/Coq-Au-Vin-en-oatskoekies-blog-069-1024x768.jpg\" alt=\"Coq Au Vin en oatskoekies blog 069\" class=\"wp-image-1451\" loading=\"lazy\"></a></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"wp-block-paragraph\"></p>",
